28208243441472313497.Text: The Oracle has asked me to rescue Adusamsi Assurnarairan from the Dunmer stronghold of Rotheran. She went there to recover the Ice Blade of the Monarch. If possible, I'm to recover the Ice Blade of the Monarch, and bring that to back to the Oracle.

153823842789211859.Text: The Oracle had already heard from Adusamsi Assurnarairan about her rescue. Adusamsi sent me her enchanted ring as a token of her gratitude. The Oracle suggested I should keep the Ice Blade of the Monarch if I should find it. She thanked me, and told me to speak to her when I am ready for another of the Oracle's Quests.

13083297161004913299.Text: The Oracle had already heard from Adusamsi Assurnarairan about her rescue. Adusamsi sent me her enchanted ring as a token of her gratitude. The Oracle suggested I should keep the Ice Blade of the Monarch and dedicate it to the service of the Imperial cult. She thanked me, and told me to speak to her when I am ready for another of the Oracle's Quests.

1904209741575318205.Text: Imperial Cult: Ice Blade of the Monarch
